{"tid":1706071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【naver】IZONE X1解散？ Mnet\"沒有過解散商議\"","createTime":"2019-11-11T04:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:33:38.000Z","uid":229026,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"11f81c353ee1f57cd91e6216dc2855a256309461","tid":1706071,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"Mnet produce系列誕生的組合IZONE和X1的解散說擴散，對此Mnet表示了沒有對於解散的商議以及會繼續觀察調查結果的基本立場<br />\nMnet方有關人員於11日稱雖然IZONE新專輯回歸暫定延期，但對於解散並沒有過討論。<br />\n接著說道，對於IZONE和X1之後活動的議論的確在進行中，但還沒有具體決定下來的結果，是在繼續觀察調查情況中的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好擔心佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經幾日無出mail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251d4ba88c013a8138e5761ac776ac5cb355c0c4","tid":1706071,"uid":46435,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"收到phone佢地係宿舍咸左幾日 成日笑果幾個咸得最勁.."},{"pid":"71edf604e1115cd3a2e9abd96976627345add567","tid":1706071,"uid":74278,"like":20,"dislike":9,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"事鳩旦啦屌你老母仲追乜撚野韓星呀仆街"},{"pid":"cdd335bb1cd2ba4e4760c62dbfbea51ef5058acd","tid":1706071,"uid":48132,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"捉曹柔理上前線做盾擋tg啦<br />\n<br />\n面皮咁厚"},{"pid":"a3e880e9bf7558fef6017e2d091e8f2a7d327535","tid":1706071,"uid":323791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"今日幾點開記者會"},{"pid":"5957a7efd686cb24903014b8fc3cd7ddb04c5464","tid":1706071,"uid":229026,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"71edf604e1115cd3a2e9abd96976627345add567","tid":1706071,"uid":74278,"like":20,"dislike":9,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"事鳩旦啦屌你老母仲追乜撚野韓星呀仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"屌人老母 （革命分 +10）<br />\n不推文 （革命分+10）"},{"pid":"efee13823f0b983f64a53ad88f6584b326f184fc","tid":1706071,"uid":229